  "keyFeatures": [
    "Fluent C# API for designing PDF layouts with clean, readable code",
    "Component-based architecture supporting reusable document fragments (IComponent, IDynamicComponent)",
    "Comprehensive layout engine with Row, Column, Table, Grid, Layers, Inlined, and MultiColumn elements",
    "Full text styling: fonts, sizes, weights, colors, spacing, RTL support, page numbers",
    "Image support: PNG, JPG, WEBP, SVG, dynamic images, and SkiaSharp integration",
    "Document operations: merge, split, overlay, underlay, encrypt/decrypt, linearize, attach files",
    "PDF/A (2b, 2u, 2a, 3b, 3u, 3a) and PDF/UA-1 compliance standards",
    "ZUGFeRD / Factur-X e-invoicing support",
    "Companion App with live hot-reload preview for rapid development",
    "Cross-platform: Windows, Linux, macOS on .NET 6+, .NET Framework 4.6.2+",
    "High performance: generates thousands of pages per second with minimal resource usage"
  ],
